(:summary    "Minor mode for spell checking"
 :created    "2006"
 :updated    "20100525"
 :license    "GPL-3"
 :authors    (("Martin Rudalics" . "rudalics@gmx.at"))
 :maintainer ("Martin Rudalics" . "rudalics@gmx.at")
 :provided   (speck)
 :required   ((("cl" cl)))
 :keywords   (checking spell)
 :wikipage   "SpeckMode"
 :commentary "\
Speck is a minor mode for \"specking\" - spell-checking text displayed
in Emacs windows.  Invoke the command `speck-mode' to toggle specking
of all windows showing the current buffer.

_____________________________________________________________________________
                                                                             
